Pinera Confirms Creation of $4 Billion Higher Education Fund

-- B y   R a n d a l l   W o o d s
-- 
2011-09-30T00:05:21Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-09-30/pinera-confirms-creation-of-4-billion-higher-education-fund.html
Chilean President Sebastian Pinera
confirmed plans to create a $4 billion education fund in a
televised speech to the nation today. Chile will ensure quality
education at a “constitutional level,” he said.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Randall Woods in Santiago at 
 rwoods13@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Philip Sanders at 
